Common Audit Findings
Severity	Description	Example
Critical	Immediate risk to the organization	Domain Admin account with no MFA
High	Serious weakness requiring prompt action	Unpatched internet-facing server
Medium	Moderate risk	Weak password policy
Low	Minor issue	Incomplete documentation
Informational	Recommendation only	Improve log retention
